{"tid":2349433,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"2020年度叱咤樂壇流行榜頒獎典禮(14)","createTime":"2021-01-01T14:25:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-01T14:44:34.000Z","uid":219010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"33ccc1f1f67832957651ebe2267dfdbf67cae66c","tid":2349433,"uid":219010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T14:25:46.000Z","msg":"2020年度叱咤樂壇流行榜頒獎典禮，是由香港商業電台舉辦的一個本地音樂頒獎典禮，將於2021年1月1日晚上7時於九龍灣國際展貿中心舉行，本屆頒獎禮雖恢復為實體形式，但將不設現場觀眾，以保持2019冠狀病毒病疫情期間的社交距離。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bq8LGKi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbq8LGKi.png&h=0380a302&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本屆主題定為「一切從音樂再開始」，美術主題為一輛叱咤火炬形狀的飛船在火星中準備起飛，帶領大家再次踏上奇妙的音樂之旅， 寓意誠邀大家一同登上飛船、重新向未知的將來出發。<br />\n<br />\n直播及轉播：<br />\n叱咤903&mdash;聲音直播<br />\n<a href=\"http://my903.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmy903.com&d=3ylU62tgaeYkhBfBjxJ1gZ1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=c534b760\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://my903.com</a>、<a href=\"http://881903.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F881903.com&d=3ylU62tgaeYkhBfBjxJ1gZ1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=8a00b7b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://881903.com</a>&mdash;網上串流視像直播<br />\n手機程式 Hong Kong Toolbar（Android 用戶）、商台節目重溫 app / Hong Kong Toolbar（iOS用戶）&mdash;影片直播<br />\nViuTV&mdash;影片轉播<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">此post為ViuTV區，網上live post請移玉步</span></strong><br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><ins>劇透撚仆街死啦</ins></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"e655fd878d7c60272cbf071806baee52040803f2","tid":2349433,"uid":219010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T14:40:30.000Z","msg":"開錯唔好推"},{"pid":"bf531ead972d4c406f5386d3b2cd8164501a618d","tid":2349433,"uid":310504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T14:44:34.000Z","msg":"會唔會又係姜B<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"e655fd878d7c60272cbf07